<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sofia Farinati | Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset e Variabili */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: '-apple-system', BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        :root {
            --bg-color: #0a0a0a;
            --text-color: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #8e8e93;
            --accent-color: #34c759; /* Cambia questo colore per personalizzare il brand */
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header / Nav */
        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 2rem 4%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 100;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.7);
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 2rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0 4%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
            line-height: 1.1;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.03eM;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .hero-cta {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background-color: var(--text-color);
            color: var(--bg-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            width: fit-content;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .hero-cta:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Sezione Progetti (Griglia stile Framer) */
        .projects {
            padding: 8rem 4%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .project-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(45%, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .project-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .project-card {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            display: block;
            group;
        }

        .project-image {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 16/10;
            background-color: #1c1c1e;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }

        /* Effetto hover sull'immagine */
        .project-card:hover .project-image {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .project-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .project-card p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            padding: 5rem 4%;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #1c1c1e;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">SOFIA FARINATI</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#projects">Progetti</a>
            <a href="#about">Info</a>
            <a href="mailto:tuamail@esempio.com">Contatto</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero" id="about">
            <h1>Visual & Digital Designer.<br><span>Creo esperienze digitali che lasciano il segno.</span></h1>
            <a href="#projects" class="hero-cta">Guarda i miei lavori</a>
        </section>

        <section class="projects" id="projects">
            <h2 class="section-title">Progetti Selezionati</h2>
            <div class="project-grid">
                
                <a href="#" class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-image">
                        </div>
                    <h3>Nome Progetto Uno</h3>
                    <p>Art Direction / Web Design</p>
                </a>

                <a href="#" class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-image"></div>
                    <h3>Nome Progetto Due</h3>
                    <p>UI/UX Design / Brand Identity</p>
                </a>

                <a href="#" class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-image"></div>
                    <h3>Nome Progetto Tre</h3>
                    <p>Motion Design</p>
                </a>

                <a href="#" class="project-card">
                    <div class="project-image"></div>
                    <h3>Nome Progetto Quattro</h3>
                    <p>Sviluppo Web / Framer</p>
                </a>

            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Sofia Farinati. Tutti i diritti riservati. Realizzato con HTML & CSS.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
